<h1>Reset your password</h1>
<p>Hi <strong style="color:#F0F0F0;">{{fullName}}</strong>,</p>
<p>
  We received a request to reset the password for your NduthiRide account.
  Click the button below to choose a new password.
</p>

<p style="text-align:center; margin: 32px 0;">
  <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="btn">Reset Password</a>
</p>

<div class="alert">
  <strong>This link expires in {{expiresMins}} minutes.</strong><br />
  If you did not request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
  Your password will remain unchanged.
</div>

<hr class="divider" />

<p>If the button above does not work, copy and paste this URL into your browser:</p>
<p style="font-size:13px; color:#555; word-break:break-all;">{{resetUrl}}</p>

<hr class="divider" />

<p style="font-size: 13px; color: #555; text-align: center;">
  For your security, this link can only be used once and expires after {{expiresMins}} minutes.
</p>
